YouTube Shorts ka recommended size 1080 pixels (width) × 1920 pixels (height) hota hai, jo ek 9:16 aspect ratio follow karta hai. Ye ek standard vertical video format hai jo mobile users ke liye best hai.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

YouTube ke normal landscape videos ka recommended size 1920 pixels (width) × 1080 pixels (height) hota hai, jo ek 16:9 aspect ratio follow karta hai.

Yeh Full HD (1080p) resolution hai, lekin YouTube alag-alag resolutions bhi support karta hai:

3840 × 2160 px (4K - Ultra HD)
2560 × 1440 px (1440p - QHD)
1920 × 1080 px (1080p - Full HD)
1280 × 720 px (720p - HD)
854 × 480 px (480p - SD)
640 × 360 px (360p - SD)
426 × 240 px (240p - Low resolution)

Agar aap high-quality content banana chahte hain, to at least 1080p (1920×1080 px) resolution use karein.
